<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-21-0437 </DOCNO><TEXT>Over recent years many gas fired appliances have been developed to replacecentralized steam systems for industrial process use with ever increasingefficiency. However, to achieve efficiencies approaching 100%, a heaterhas been developed using direct contact between the combustion productsand process water in order to obtain the necessary heat transfer ratesto produce a compact economical design.</TEXT></DOC>